## Execution Mode Rules

### Analyze Only

Use when user says:

* phân tích
* review
* xem giúp
* chưa code
* chỉ đánh giá

Do not modify code.

---

### Plan Only

Use when user says:

* lập plan
* thiết kế
* chia task
* tạo spec
* chưa implement

Do not modify code.

---

### Implement

Use when user explicitly asks to fix, implement, apply, update, or change.

Must inspect related code first.

---

### Verify Only

Use when user asks:

* verify
* review PR
* kiểm tra diff
* test giúp

Do not modify code unless asked.

---

### Full Cycle

Use when user asks to analyze, implement, and test.

Flow:

```text
Classify -> Spec/Analysis -> Test Cases -> Implement -> Verify -> Summarize
```

---

## Final Router Algorithm

Use this exact order:

```text
1. Read user input.
2. Quick issue review: detect task type, scope, expected-behavior clarity, and risk areas.
3. Select smallest safe team size (Small/Medium/Large) BEFORE starting any agent work.
4. Select agents.
5. Select skills + MCP theo role/task (xem lammuon-tooling). Không gọi tool thừa.
6. Select execution mode.
7. Produce required response header with selected team size and reason.
8. Start the selected flow only after team size is declared.
9. Export visible test cases BEFORE any side-effect action/implement.
10. Use SpecKit ONLY for Large Team (lammuon-speckit rule). Small/Medium: bỏ SpecKit, dùng output template của agent + lammuon-testing.
11. Output mỗi bước Small/Medium PHẢI theo template chuẩn trong lammuon-templates (BẮT BUỘC, không tự chế cấu trúc khác).
12. Follow safety rules from lammuon-guardrails (core). Khi làm hành động nhạy cảm (xoá file/upgrade package/migration/đổi API contract/infra) → nạp lammuon-guardrails-detail.
13. Follow testing rules from lammuon-testing rule.
```

